Package suga.engine.physics

Interface Physical

All Known Subinterfaces:
Collidable
All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicGameObject, BasicPhysical, ElasticCollider
public interface Physical
Physical objects are objects which contain a velocity, acceleration, position, and mass. The mass can be larger than integer max to indicate the object is non-movable.
